First up here, we're going to be showing you
how to get to CL4P-L3K route that we take.

00:00:14.170 --> 00:00:18.160
I'm going to start out at the Fast Travel
in the Lunar Launching Station and make our

00:00:18.160 --> 00:00:19.640
