00:00:27.619 --> 00:00:32.449
So let's talk about the 3DD1.E or better know
as Eddie Oz Kit.

00:00:32.449 --> 00:00:37.359
This is a Legendary Oz Kit that is pretty
much hands down one of the best Oz Kits in

00:00:37.359 --> 00:00:39.000
the game.

00:00:39.000 --> 00:00:44.900
And one of the best things about it is unlike
many other things, you can actually farm for

00:00:44.900 --> 00:00:45.900
this item.

00:00:45.900 --> 00:00:49.250
But you have to do something very particular.

00:00:49.250 --> 00:00:55.449
You have to complete the Eradicate Mission
in a very particular way.

00:00:55.449 --> 00:00:58.950
When you get to the end of the Eradicate mission,
you're going to have the choice to either

00:00:58.950 --> 00:01:02.360
destroy CL4P-L3K or secure CL4P-L3K.

00:01:02.360 --> 00:01:07.780
And you secure him by hitting the little console
and it's going to secure the doors and lock

00:01:07.780 --> 00:01:09.130
him inside.

00:01:09.130 --> 00:01:17.090
This is the choice that you have to choose
if you want to farm for the 3DD1.E later on.

00:01:17.090 --> 00:01:20.979
If you kill CL4P-L3K, you will not be able
to farm.

00:01:20.979 --> 00:01:23.250
He will not respawn again.

00:01:23.250 --> 00:01:28.760
Also, you'll notice if you secure him in here,
that one of the even better things, you'll

00:01:28.760 --> 00:01:33.649
get a double farm for your money because when
you come back down here, CL4P-L3K will be

00:01:33.649 --> 00:01:40.720
down here and he drops the 3DD1.E and you
can also farm Eghood who drops the Blowfly.

00:01:40.720 --> 00:01:47.170
Which by the way, is a pretty frickin nice
gun to come back here with and kill CL4P-L3K

00:01:47.170 --> 00:01:48.450
since it's corrosive.

